sources.title: Hollows Grove | Full Horror Movie | Lance Henriksen | Mykelti Williamson
sources.description:
Hollows Grove - A young filmmaker documents his ghost-hunting, reality show friends as their routine investigation of an abandoned orphanage turns into a nightmare from which they can't escape.
2014. Stars: Mykelti Williamson, Lance Henriksen, Matthew Carey
